latestIgtvVideos.title: Just a random thought on social media hate
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey everyone, so since a lot of you asked me to post one consolidated video, therefore I took down the stories and am posting it here as an IGTV.  Please excuse if you think that the video is not consolidated or not edited properly as I just shot it randomly on my stories when I woke up today morning but do know that this is something that I really have wanted to put out there since a long time now! 
Yesterday it was my mother's birthday and it was Father's day. I love my father beyond words and I don't think it needs to be justified or should be judged whether or not I posted something here. Please note that This is NOT something that is coming out as a reaction to that only one DM. But it has happened so many times before. If you post about a public issue, you get bashed, if you don't, then people are quick to brand you with a number of labels.
 I just decided to make this because I think it goes out for not just me but for a lot of people out there! There is already a lot of panic, stress and anxiety that has gripped each one of us and a little concern and putting a little check on your words before you put them out there can go a long way.
